Map Features:
=============

- Armory
- 30 CT Spawns
- 30 T Spawns
- 12 Jail Cells
- VIP
- Medic
- Solitary
- Outside
- Soccer
- Kitchen
- Cafeteria
- Soccer/Football
- Disco
- LR Room
- Big Cage
- Library
- Pool
- Showers
- Nade Toss
- Tic-Tac-Toe
- Torture Room
- Dodgeball
- Roulette Pit
- Various Vents/Teleports
- Much More

This is the second version of my first ever map.  I always appreciate any questions/comments/concerns.
Any feedback is helpful and will be taken constructively as I attempt to become better at mapping.


INSTALLATION
============

Install the .bsp into your maps folder commonly found in the following directory:

C:\Program Files(x86)\Steam\SteamApps\yourusername\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps

There shouldn't be anything else you need besides that.
